> _dir/.../ + $output_dir/gph_files/.../
.         log on master
.         di as text "  [OK]  do/va/reg_out_va_dk_all_fig.do"
.         log off master
. 
.         * RELOCATED 2026-05-08 per plan v3 §3.3 step 3 batch 3d — sibling-lag
